haw.livingplace.scriptSimulator

Class ScriptSimulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • haw.livingplace.scriptSimulator.ScriptSimulator

  • public class ScriptSimulator
extends java.lang.Object
    Main class for the Scriptsimulator. The ScriptSimulator will initialize everything that is needed for proper execution end will open the GUI.
    Author:
    Andreas Basener
